\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
二分法的迭代过程没有考虑
\begin_inset Formula $f(a)$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $f(b)$
\end_inset

的大小.
 试值法认为, 如果在等分区间的过程中, 比如, 如果
\begin_inset Formula $f(a)$
\end_inset

比
\begin_inset Formula $f(b)$
\end_inset

更接近于0, 则根有可能更靠近
\begin_inset Formula $f(a)$
\end_inset

.
 因此, 试值法用过
\begin_inset Formula $f(a)$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $f(b)$
\end_inset

割线的交点代替区间中点.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设
\begin_inset Formula $f(a)f(b)<0$
\end_inset

, 过点
\begin_inset Formula $(a,f(a))$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $(b,f(b))$
\end_inset

的割线
\begin_inset Formula $L$
\end_inset

与
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

轴交点
\begin_inset Formula $(c,0)$
\end_inset

.
  
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
我们知道, 经过点
\begin_inset Formula $(a,f(a))$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $(b,f(b))$
\end_inset

的割线是
\begin_inset Formula $f(b)=\frac{f(b)-f(a)}{b-a}(x-b).$
\end_inset

 令
\begin_inset Formula $y=0,$
\end_inset

就有
\begin_inset Formula $x=b-\frac{f(b)(b-a)}{f(b)-f(a)}.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
试值法的过程只要把上述二分法第一步改为
\begin_inset Formula $\boxed{x=b-\frac{f(b)(b-a)}{f(b)-f(a)}=\frac{a_{n}f(b_{n})-b_{n}f(a_{n})}{f(b_{n})-f(a_{n})}}$
\end_inset

 即可.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
下面探讨试值法的收敛性.
 实际上可构造一系列
\begin_inset Formula $\{[a_{n},b_{n}]\}$
\end_inset

区间序列, 其中每个序列都包含零点.
 上面提到在每一步中, 零点
\begin_inset Formula $r$
\end_inset

的近似值为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
c_{n}=b_{n}-f(b_{n})\frac{b_{n}-a_{n}}{f(b_{n})-f(a_{n})}=\red{\frac{a_{n}f(b_{n})-b_{n}f(a_{n})}{f(b_{n})-f(a_{n})}}.
\]

\end_inset

迭代许多轮之后, 我们说
\begin_inset Formula $a_{k},b_{k}$
\end_inset

将会靠得很近, 所以我们采用红色的式子进行计算, 来避免丢失精度.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
实际上, 试值法碰到“不动点”的时候, 可能越来越慢, 甚至还不如二分法 ; 另外尽管区间宽度
\begin_inset Formula $b_{n}-a_{n}$
\end_inset

越来越小, 但可能不趋近于零, 无法作为终止判别条件.
 因此就需要根据
\begin_inset Formula $\delta$
\end_inset

来判别.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
迭代法简介
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
迭代法的收敛性
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection
是否收敛
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
设
\begin_inset Formula $g(x)$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $[a,b]$
\end_inset

上连续可导, 对
\begin_inset Formula $\forall x\in[a,b]$
\end_inset

,若:  
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Enumerate
\begin_inset Formula $g(x)\in[a,b]$
\end_inset

 (映内性),
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
\begin_inset Formula $|g'(x)|\leq L<1$
\end_inset

 (压缩性, 
\begin_inset Formula $L$
\end_inset

为常数, 称为压缩系数).
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
那么
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
函数
\begin_inset Formula $f(x)=x-g(x)$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $[a,b]$
\end_inset

上有唯一零点
\begin_inset Formula $x^{*}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
对于任意初值
\begin_inset Formula $x_{0}\in[a,b]$
\end_inset

, 迭代公式
\begin_inset Formula $x_{k+1}=g(x_{k})$
\end_inset

均收敛于方程的根
\begin_inset Formula $x^{*}$
\end_inset

；
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
迭代误差可用如下两个等价的不等式来估计:
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
|x_{k}-x^{*}| & \leq\frac{L}{1-L}|x_{k}-x_{k-1}|\\
|x_{k}-x^{*}| & \leq\frac{L^{k}}{1-L}|x_{1}-x_{0}|
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Standard
其证明大致思路只要使用Lagrange中值定理即可.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
\begin_inset Formula $x^{3}+4x^{2}-10=0$
\end_inset

在[1,2]上有一个根(正根), 分析
\begin_inset Formula $g(x)=\frac{1}{2}(10-x^{3})^{\frac{1}{2}}$
\end_inset

的收敛性.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
求导得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
g^{\prime}=-\frac{3x^{2}}{4\sqrt{10-x^{3}}}\quad g^{\prime\prime}=-\left(\frac{3x}{2\sqrt{10-x^{3}}}+\frac{9x^{4}}{8\sqrt{\left(10-x^{3}\right)^{3}}}\right),
\]

\end_inset

显然, 在此区间上
\begin_inset Formula $g'(x)$
\end_inset

、
\begin_inset Formula $g''(x)$
\end_inset

均
\begin_inset Formula $<0$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $g(x)$
\end_inset

、
\begin_inset Formula $g'(x)$
\end_inset

均为减函数.
 考虑
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
映内性: 
\begin_inset Formula $g(1)=3/2\in[1,2]$
\end_inset

, 但
\begin_inset Formula $g(2)=\sqrt{2}/2\approx0.7071\notin[1,2]$
\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
压缩性: 
\begin_inset Formula $|g'(1)|=0.25<1$
\end_inset

, 但
\begin_inset Formula $|g'(2)|\approx2.12>1$
\end_inset

.
  
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
均不满足收敛条件.
 但是考虑子区间[1, 1.5], 上述两个条件均满足了.
 
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Standard
收敛定理有了, 满足定理的两个条件不容易.
 下面我们探讨一种在某一点附近收敛的情况.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Definition
若存在
\begin_inset Formula $g(x)$
\end_inset

的不动点
\begin_inset Formula $x^{*}$
\end_inset

及其某个邻域
\begin_inset Formula $N(x^{*},\delta):=[x^{*}-\delta,x^{*}+\delta]$
\end_inset

, 使得
\begin_inset Formula $\forall x_{0}\in N$
\end_inset

,由迭代公式生成的序列
\begin_inset Formula $\{x_{k}\}(\{x_{k}\}\subset N)$
\end_inset

 收敛于
\begin_inset Formula $x^{*}$
\end_inset

,则称迭代公式局部收敛.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
设
\begin_inset Formula $x^{*}$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $g(x)$
\end_inset

的不动点, 
\begin_inset Formula $g^{\prime}(x)$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $x^{*}$
\end_inset

的某个邻域上连续, 且 
\begin_inset Formula $|g^{\prime}(x^{*})|<1$
\end_inset

,则迭代公式局部收敛.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
证明可以使用连续函数的定义和Lagrange中值定理得到.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
但是, 
\begin_inset Formula $x^{*}$
\end_inset

本身就是待求的, 如何判断
\begin_inset Formula $|g'(x^{*})|<1$
\end_inset

呢? 实际上, 
\begin_inset Formula $g'(x)$
\end_inset

的连续性表明: 如果
\begin_inset Formula $g(x)$
\end_inset

迭代收敛到
\begin_inset Formula $x^{*}$
\end_inset

, 在
\begin_inset Formula $x^{*}$
\end_inset

的某个邻域内就应该有
\begin_inset Formula $|g'(x)|<1$
\end_inset

.
 在应用中, 如已知
\begin_inset Formula $x^{*}$
\end_inset

的大致位置, 而
\begin_inset Formula $x_{0}$
\end_inset

为
\begin_inset Formula $x^{*}$
\end_inset

的一个较好的近似值, 可用
\begin_inset Formula $|g'(x_{0})|<1$
\end_inset

代替
\begin_inset Formula $|g'(x^{*})|<1$
\end_inset

, 这就可以判定上述迭代公式的收敛性.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection
收敛速度
\end_layout

\begin_layout Definition
设迭代
\begin_inset Formula $x_{k+1}=g(x_{k})$
\end_inset

收敛到
\begin_inset Formula $g(x)$
\end_inset

的不动点
\begin_inset Formula $x^{*}$
\end_inset

.
 记绝对误差
\begin_inset Formula $e_{k}=x_{k}-x^{*}$
\end_inset

.
 若
\begin_inset Formula $\lim_{k\to\infty}\left|\frac{e_{k+1}}{e_{k}^{p}}\right|=C\neq0\text{ }(C\text{为常数)}$
\end_inset

, 则称该迭代为以收敛阶
\begin_inset Formula $p$
\end_inset

收敛到
\begin_inset Formula $x^{*}$
\end_inset

.
 数
\begin_inset Formula $C$
\end_inset

称为渐近误差常数.
  
\end_layout

\begin_layout Definition
更进一步, 当
\begin_inset Formula $p=1$
\end_inset

时称为线性收敛; 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Definition
当 
\begin_inset Formula $p>1$
\end_inset

 时称为超线性收敛.
 当
\begin_inset Formula $p=2$
\end_inset

时称为二次(阶)收敛（或平方收敛） .
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Remark*
实际上, 不动点迭代中, 若迭代数列
\begin_inset Formula $\{x_{k}\}$
\end_inset

收敛, 且 
\begin_inset Formula $g'(x)\neq0$
\end_inset

, 则
\begin_inset Formula $e_{k+1}=x_{k+1}-x^{*}=g(x_{k})-g(x^{*})=g'(\xi)e_{k}$
\end_inset

.
 取极限得 
\begin_inset Formula $\lim_{n\to\infty}|e_{k+1}/e_{k}|=|g'(x^{*})|\neq0$
\end_inset

, 这就表明其线性收敛.
 实际上要想得到超线性收敛,就必然满足
\begin_inset Formula $g'(x^{*})=0$
\end_inset

.
 并且可以看出来线性收敛的时候
\begin_inset Formula $|C|<1$
\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Newton迭代法
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection
基本思想
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
在学习微积分的时候我们知道性质还不算差的函数可以被线性近似, 即
\begin_inset Formula $f(x)\approx f(x_{k})+f'(x_{k})(x-x_{k}).$
\end_inset

 当
\begin_inset Formula $f'(x_{k})\neq0$
\end_inset

时, 
\begin_inset Formula $f(x)=0$
\end_inset

可用此线性方程(切线)近似代替, 即 
\begin_inset Formula $f(x_{k})+f'(x_{k})(x^{*}-x_{k})\approx0$
\end_inset

.
 解这个方程, 就得到了迭代公式
\begin_inset Formula $x^{*}\approx x_{k}-\frac{f(x_{k})}{f'(x_{k})}.$
\end_inset

 使左端取得
\begin_inset Formula $x_{k+1},$
\end_inset

就得到了
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\boxed{x_{k+1}\approx x_{k}-\frac{f(x_{k})}{f^{\prime}(x_{k})},k=0,1,2,\cdots}
\]

\end_inset

这就是Newton迭代公式.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection
收敛情况
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Newton 迭代法在单根情形下至少二阶收敛.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
试说明: 设
\begin_inset Formula $f(x)$
\end_inset

在零点
\begin_inset Formula $x^{*}$
\end_inset

的邻域内
\begin_inset Formula $f''$
\end_inset

连续,则牛顿迭代公式在
\begin_inset Formula $x^{*}$
\end_inset

是单根的情况下至少平方局部收敛.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
先证局部收敛: Newton法 可 写 成 不 动 点 迭 代 的 形 式 :
\begin_inset Formula $x_{k+1}=\varphi(x_{k})=x_{k}-\frac{f(x_{k})}{f^{\prime}(x_{k})}.$
\end_inset

 若
\begin_inset Formula $x^{*}$
\end_inset

是方程
\begin_inset Formula $f(x)=0\text{的单根}f(x^{*})=0$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $f^{\prime}(x^{*})\neq0\Rightarrow x^{*}=\varphi(x^{*}).$
\end_inset

 所以
\begin_inset Formula $x^{*}$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi(x)$
\end_inset

的不动点.
 又
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\varphi^{\prime}(x)=1-\frac{[f^{\prime}(x)]^{2}-f(x)f^{\prime\prime}(x)}{\left[f^{\prime}(x)\right]^{2}}=\frac{f(x)f^{\prime\prime}(x)}{\left[f^{\prime}(x)\right]^{2}}\Rightarrow\varphi^{\prime}(x^{*})=0.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
再证至少收敛阶
\begin_inset Formula $p=2$
\end_inset

: 将
\begin_inset Formula $f(x^{*})$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $x_{k}$
\end_inset

处做一阶Taylor展开:  
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
0=f(x^{*})=f(x_{k})+f^{\prime}(x_{k})(x^{*}-x_{k})+\frac{1}{2}f^{\prime\prime}(\xi)(x^{*}-x_{k})^{2}
\]

\end_inset

因为没有重根, 
\begin_inset Formula $f^{\prime}(x_{k})\neq0$
\end_inset

, 等式两边同时除以
\begin_inset Formula $f^{\prime}(x_{k})$
\end_inset

, 得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{aligned} & x_{k}-x^{*}=\frac{f(x_{k})}{f^{\prime}(x_{k})}+\frac{f^{\prime\prime}(\xi)}{2f^{\prime}(x_{k})}\left(x^{*}-x_{k}\right)^{2}\\
\Rightarrow & x_{k}-\frac{f(x_{k})}{f'(x_{k})}-x^{*}=\frac{f''(\xi)}{2f'(x_{k})}{\left(x^{*}-x_{k}\right)}^{2}\\
\Rightarrow & x_{k+1}-x^{*}=\frac{f''(\xi)}{2f'(x_{k})}(x^{*}-x_{k})^{2}\\
\Rightarrow & \lim_{k\to\infty}\frac{|e_{k+1}|}{\left|e_{k}\right|^{2}}=\lim_{k\to\infty}\frac{|x^{*}-x_{k+1}|}{\left|x^{*}-x_{k}\right|^{2}}=\frac{|f^{\prime\prime}(x^{*})|}{2|f^{\prime}(x^{*})|}=c\neq0
\end{aligned}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
所以Newton迭代法(单根的情况下)至少二阶局部收敛.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
Newton法也适用于求重根的情形, 但是收敛速度会变慢.
 实际上当
\begin_inset Formula $x^{*}$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $f(x$
\end_inset

)的
\begin_inset Formula $m(m>1)$
\end_inset

重根时, 
\begin_inset Formula $f(x)$
\end_inset

可以表示为: 
\begin_inset Formula $f(x)=(x-x^{*})^{m}g(x)\text{ (其中}g(x^{*})\neq0)$
\end_inset

, 迭代公式变为
\begin_inset Formula $x_{k+1}=x_{k}-\frac{f(x_{k})}{f^{\prime}(x_{k})}=x_{k}-\frac{(x_{k}-x^{*})g(x_{k})}{mg(x_{k})+(x_{k}-x^{*})g^{\prime}(x_{k})}$
\end_inset

.
 令
\begin_inset Formula $e_{k}=x_{k}-x^{*}$
\end_inset

, 则将上式两边同减
\begin_inset Formula $x^{*}$
\end_inset

, 得
\begin_inset Formula $e_{k+1}=x_{k+1}-x^{*}=e_{k}-\frac{e_{k}g(x_{k})}{mg(x_{k})+e_{k}g^{\prime}(x_{k})}$
\end_inset

.
 两边同时除以
\begin_inset Formula $e_{k}$
\end_inset

, 取极限, 得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\lim_{k\to\infty}\frac{e_{k+1}}{e_{k}}=\lim_{k\to\infty}\left(1-\frac{g(x_{k})}{mg(x_{k})+e_{k}g^{\prime}(x_{k})}\right)=1-\frac{1}{m}\neq0
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
这表明牛顿法求方程的重根时仅为线性收敛.
 并且
\begin_inset Formula $m$
\end_inset

重数越高, 收敛越慢.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
割线法
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
由于 Newton 迭代法每次迭代都要计算导数
\begin_inset Formula $f'(x_{k})$
\end_inset

, 当
\begin_inset Formula $f(x)$
\end_inset

较复杂时, 计算量大.
 下面考察一种避免导数运算的求根方法.
 在迭代过程中用到前两步
\begin_inset Formula $x_{k}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $x_{k-1}$
\end_inset

处的函数值构造迭代函数来提高迭代的收敛速度.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
虽说不必计算
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $x_{k}$
\end_inset

处的导数, 但是也应该有和导数一样的类似物.
 我们考虑两个点
\begin_inset Formula $x_{k},x_{k-1}$
\end_inset

之间的差商
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{f(x_{k})-f(x_{k-1})}{x_{k}-x_{k-1}},$
\end_inset

并用这个来近似替代替代牛顿公式中的点
\begin_inset Formula $x_{k}$
\end_inset

处的导数
\begin_inset Formula $f'(x_{k})$
\end_inset

, 得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
x_{k+1}=x_{k}-\frac{f(x_{k})}{f(x_{k})-f(x_{k-1})}(x_{k}-x_{k-1}),k=1,2,3,\cdots.
\]

\end_inset

这称为割线迭代公式, 相应的迭代法称为割线法、弦截 (两步)法或多点迭代法.
  
\end_layout

